Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty easy once you know how to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.93,0:00:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can lose now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.51,0:00:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have that. You wanted it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to owe you anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.24,0:00:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're even now, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.88,0:00:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.23,0:00:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.06,0:01:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.82,0:01:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a little tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.91,0:01:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't force yourself, I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.98,0:01:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That idiot.
