Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.56,0:02:54.32,EPISODE TITLE,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(236,0)\c&HFBFCFE&\3c&HFBFCFE&\pos(338,481)}Episode 8   I'm such an idiot
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.70,0:03:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.25,0:03:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't fight like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.99,0:03:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just lying when you say you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.34,0:03:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so painful to watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because you say you're okay doesn't mean you should go all out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.89,0:03:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if I hadn't done that, I wouldn't have won.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have enough talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if you win, fighting like that isn't good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.68,0:03:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:04:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already gotten this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.28,0:04:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could I possibly do for myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I can do now is kill Witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm merely a rock with no other purpose in life—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a corpse that walks around, pretending to be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.35,0:04:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could someone do to help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think about it, there's no purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could I do to make you happy, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You would need to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.83,0:04:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyubei already told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the most talented out of all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to work as hard as I do in order to defeat Witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.73,0:04:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.52,0:04:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you just say you wanted to do something for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try being in my position, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.73,0:04:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You obviously can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.91,0:05:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't give up your humanity out of pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not pity...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can do anything, yet you refuse to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why {\i1}I{\i0} have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.41,0:05:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just sit back spouting those empty words.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.03,0:05:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:20.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so stupid! Why the hell did I say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.41,0:05:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do anything for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:48.24,(05:48 sign),,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\pos(301,357)}Homura
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:06:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Walpurgis Night is predicted to appear around this perimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.06,0:06:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What makes you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.58,0:06:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Statistics.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Statistics?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't heard anything about Walpurgis coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.73,0:06:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you calculate these statistics, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.84,0:06:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither of us trusts the other,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but could you at least tell me a little bit more?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to know as well, Akemi Homura.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the fuck are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.80,0:06:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I came uninvited.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've come here tonight to report some information to you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.53,0:06:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miki Sayaka's exhaustion is rapidly piling up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her ability to use magic hasn't changed, but it seems she's carrying a curse now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And whose fault do you think that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:07:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, we'll be dealing with something before Walpurgis Night even comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two should be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.83,0:07:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you be asking her that instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fairly certain that you're aware of this already, Akemi Homura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.42,0:07:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.12,0:07:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd really like to know where you get all this information from.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.47,0:07:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've already told us what you wanted to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.58,0:07:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just gonna let him go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.34,0:07:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing will happen if I kill him.{dunno if you refer to QB as "it"}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.61,0:07:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, he said something bad was going to happen involving Miki Sayaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.11,0:07:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her Soul Gem has gathered too much filth.{impurities, filth, sin, thanks for adding this to the consistency file ya moron}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't purify it in time, the damage will be too much to reverse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:57.74,(05:48 sign),,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\pos(301,357)\c&H031C2F&}Homura
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The auxiliary verb, "must," means something that you are required to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.89,0:08:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While on the other hand, "have to" has a different...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have followed her...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the way to your house, Shizuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.29,0:08:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I've ever seen you go this way before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.96,0:08:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'm actually going in the complete opposite direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, why are you going this way today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kamijo-kun...{again, kamijou or kamijo--your file sucks dick, qc-kun}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to talk to you about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? She hasn't come home yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since yesterday...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.42,0:08:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:09:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Sorry for bothering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.86,0:09:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to find her!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.43,0:10:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.22,0:10:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have much strength left. You need to fight the Witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up. This has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Soul Gem is already at its limit. If it's not purified soon, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no time to interrogate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you so unwilling to receive aid?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.33,0:10:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be a different Magical Girl than the rest of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.84,0:10:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not fraternize with someone who uses and discards others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.03,0:11:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need anything in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.91,0:11:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't use my magic to benefit only myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would only die when I become unable to kill Witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, I'll be completely useless, won't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.26,0:11:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.06,0:11:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This world doesn't need me if I'm unable to kill Witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.90,0:11:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you saying that? I just want to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.67,0:11:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.27,0:11:34.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.47,0:11:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you're a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look like you've already given up on everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.51,0:11:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you can do now is speak empty words.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.11,0:11:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it the same now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.23,0:11:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say you want to help me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.97,0:11:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you're actually thinking about something else, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can see right through that act.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.99,0:12:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And because of that, you'll continue hurting Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.52,0:12:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This has nothing to do with Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.33,0:12:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. All of this is for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sharp, I'll give you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you caught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really want to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.25,0:12:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want Madoka to see you destroy yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.63,0:12:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't accept my help, then you'll die either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you continue to hurt Madoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I might as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.60,0:12:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...kill you here and now,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miki Sayaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.86,0:12:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, get out of here! Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.92,0:13:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you want to help her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.03,0:13:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.93,0:13:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see. As long as I hold you like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.99,0:13:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you can't use that weird move of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.37,0:13:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them give you some weird excuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.39,0:13:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She needs to pay you back in full, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Women are retarded. You give them some money and they use it to buy some stupid shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.72,0:13:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, man. We can't treat them as people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.78,0:13:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to train them like they're a dog or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty sure she'll like that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.77,0:13:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just threaten to slap the shit out of them, that'll shut them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.45,0:14:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, the second you start being nice, they start talking about getting married or some shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be too nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.89,0:14:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that cabaret girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.25,0:14:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think she'll be making the same amount ten years from now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.76,0:14:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She needs to learn her place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then they start moping around when you ditch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.84,0:14:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good at dealing with that, right, Shou-san? Must be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.69,0:14:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to learn how...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, tell me more about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman you were just talking about; tell me more about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.86,0:14:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, kid, you're still in middle school, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.65,0:14:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be out this late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.03,0:14:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That person must have cared about you and wanted to make you happy, so she tried her best, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.81,0:14:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You knew that, though, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.99,0:14:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet you compare her to a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to thank her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.49,0:14:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just going to ditch her because she's useless?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is this? A friend of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.43,0:14:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Is this world really worth protecting?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was I fighting for? Please, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.32,0:14:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.48,0:15:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Sayaka-chan...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.48,0:15:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hate me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.85,0:15:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I hated you, would you change Sayaka-chan back to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.98,0:15:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't. I don't have the power to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.84,0:15:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you said that I could become a really powerful Magical Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.09,0:15:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Powerful" is an understatement to say the least.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can become a Magical Girl like no other.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe even the most powerful in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I accepted that in the first place, would Sayaka-chan still have become a Magical Girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.94,0:15:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka had her wish granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.48,0:16:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's completely unrelated to you, Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why me...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.33,0:16:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.06,0:16:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, your power's capability is so great that, theoretically, it shouldn't be possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like an explanation, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that power was released, then we wouldn't be discussing miracles,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.18,0:16:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but instead, the possibility of changing this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.75,0:16:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't know why you're the only one with such potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.05,0:16:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always thought of myself as a person without any redeeming qualities.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help others, I can't achieve anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.61,0:16:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll just continue to live until I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.03,0:16:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And though it's regrettable, and though it makes me feel sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.54,0:16:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.32,0:16:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reality seems to have turned out to be different.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.43,0:17:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka, if you wished for it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.24,0:17:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you could even become an omnipotent god.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.99,0:17:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.54,0:17:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I could do the things you can't, Kyubei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.61,0:17:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I formed a contract with you, could I return Sayaka-chan back to normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.88,0:17:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you could easily do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.09,0:17:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that wish worthy enough for you to give up your soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.65,0:17:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's for Sayaka-chan, then yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll become a Magical Girl—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's horrible! You didn't have to kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why... must you always sacrifice yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say you can't help anyone, or that you're worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say such things that depreciate yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.01,0:18:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about the people who care about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.10,0:18:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are people who would be sad if you're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't you realize that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.66,0:18:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about the people who wanted to protect you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.74,0:18:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Homura-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have we...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.79,0:18:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have we met before?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.44,0:18:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.59,0:18:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to go find Sayaka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.40,0:18:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... It's already too late for Miki Sayaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.55,0:18:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.52,0:18:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.42,0:18:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.82,0:19:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that was useless, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.24,0:19:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't learn, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I have a lot of replacements,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,having one destroyed for no reason is pretty troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's such a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.33,0:19:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the second time you've killed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.15,0:19:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now I know what sort of technique you use.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.47,0:19:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was time-manipulating magic, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.63,0:19:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought. I had a feeling from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.57,0:19:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not someone from this timeline, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.51,0:19:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know who you really are and what you're planning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That explains why you're trying so hard to interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.49,0:20:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to change Kaname Madoka's fate that much?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'm not going to let you get your way,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.88,0:20:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyubei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.93,0:20:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I call you... Incubator.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.82,0:20:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how long do you plan on being stubborn for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.51,0:20:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I wasted your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.40,0:20:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? That's not something you'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess. That's because I don't care anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.69,0:20:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is important to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.21,0:20:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it I want to protect?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.14,0:20:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.94,0:21:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The balance between hope and despair remains at zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that before, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.42,0:21:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand what you meant by that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.86,0:21:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I saved a few people,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.78,0:21:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the more people I save, the more hate and anger fills my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I even hurt my best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka, don't tell me you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When wishing for someone else's happiness,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.62,0:21:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,someone must be cursed in order to keep the balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.79,0:21:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how Magical Girls work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.71,0:21:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.60,0:21:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...such an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.09,0:22:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.93,0:22:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This country calls maturing women "girls," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.45,0:22:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're all going to be Witches someday,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.08,0:22:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it'd make sense to call you "Magical Girls" first.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.44,0:23:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may think I'm stupid,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.19,0:24:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I won't give up until we know she can't be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.65,0:24:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let that happen.
